# Add images + information

When the user says **add images information**, **@add-images-information**, or
supplies a taxon metadata block together with by-taxon screenshots (folder name =
`pollen_key`), follow `.cursor/skills/add-images-information/SKILL.md`
end-to-end. Do not skip rename, YAML fields, species page update, or validation.

For multi-taxon batch queues, Kerkvliet inject, or rename-only work, use
**add-pollen** (`.cursor/skills/add-pollen/SKILL.md`) instead.
